  "description": "We've introduced new smart values to refer to the manager of a Jira work item reporter or assignee. For example, you could use these smart values to automatically set the approver of a Jira work item to the assignee’s or reporter’s manager. The new smart values include issue.reporter.manager or issue.assignee.manager. Check the manager you want to refer to is set up through User Provisioning.\n\tSet up an approver workflow for Jira or Jira Service Management.\n\tOpen the automation rule builder in J",
